      <review reviewedMajorRelease="3" reviewedMinorRelease="0" reviewedMajorRevision="11" reviewedMinorRevision="4" reviewerId="c4597934-ecac-422c-b431-382e85fdcb83" reviewerName="[System]" reviewerEmail="support@ecoinvent.org" reviewDate="2011-09-28">
        <otherDetails xml:lang="en">Validation warnings:

- Consider if it would be better to create this dataset as a child dataset relative to a parent dataset. See the ecoinvent Data Quality Guideline Chapter 4.2 for further advice.
