      </review>
      <review reviewedMajorRelease="3" reviewedMinorRelease="0" reviewedMajorRevision="13" reviewedMinorRevision="15" reviewerId="9a963412-20a7-428b-8740-3582e217c4b6" reviewerName="Carl Vadenbo" reviewerEmail="vadenbo@ifu.baug.ethz.ch" reviewDate="2012-06-29">
        <details>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">In preparation for the release of ecoinvent v3.0, the datasets 'operation, average train BE' and 'transport, average train BE'  in ecoinvent v2.2 were merged into the dataset 'transport, passenger train, BE 2008'.  The amounts of the exchanges were reviewed and were found to correspond to the disaggregated datasets. The field Included Activities End and the uncertainty information need to be revised before subsequent releases of the database.  Despite this shortcoming, the new dataset was accepted for inclusion into the ecoinvent database on 2012.07.04.</text>
        </details>
        <otherDetails xml:lang="en"/>
      </review>
      <review reviewedMajorRelease="3" reviewedMinorRelease="0" reviewedMajorRevision="13" reviewedMinorRevision="15" reviewerId="c4597934-ecac-422c-b431-382e85fdcb83" reviewerName="[System]" reviewerEmail="support@ecoinvent.org" reviewDate="2012-06-29">
        <otherDetails xml:lang="en">Validation warnings:

- Consider if it would be better to create this dataset as a child dataset relative to a parent dataset. See the ecoinvent Data Quality Guideline Chapter 4.2 for further advice.
- Property 'carbon content, fossil=0,865' of master data exchange was removed from exchange 'diesel'.
